com.diagnal.engage.firebase

Class NotificationData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diagnal.engage.firebase.NotificationData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class NotificationData
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Represents the data associated with Engage push notification.
    NotificationData can be generate by calling getNotificationData(RemoteMessage), passing the RemoteMessage from firebase
